Engineering, relationship, and personal growth are challenging. | Bought a console for her partner as a gift on the 17th. Engineering studies are going well. Balancing hobbies and studies is key. | Long time no talk! We were given a new game for the console last week, it is Battlefield 1. What's been up with you? | Wow, that's a great photo! How did she show you to appreciate it? | Wow Deb, that's awesome! I'm trying to do more yoga and meditation myself to help relax and stay focused. | Gorgeous! Going for a walk and feeling so peaceful must be amazing. | That calm and peaceful feeling is so nice - it's great for recharging and thinking. | Got it! It's like hitting the refresh button and coming back even better. | Been doing it for 3 years. It's a great way to escape studying and work stress. | I'm really finding my zen again! | Thanks for your support, Deb! | Discussing the influence of loved ones and their values, emphasizing perseverance and resilience. | Teaching herself video games with support from her parents, particularly her dad and mom. | Planning to take a trip to relax and recharge after finals. | Signed up for a meditation course at a retreat near a lake. | Plans to watch the sunrise with Deborah. | Planning a camping trip to connect with nature and practice yoga, using a routine to manage a busy schedule, practicing self-care through yoga and meditation. | Traveled to a meditation retreat in Phuket for a few weeks. Experienced nature, reflection, and a break from engineering studies, which helped find inner peace. | Realized the importance of appreciating the journey and not just focusing on the finish line. | Practicing mindfulness and gratitude to boost happiness and appreciation for small moments. | Looking forward to playing the card game with Deborah. | Tried a scuba diving lesson last Friday and had an awesome time! Found a cool dive spot to explore together. | Had an awesome time at a music festival with her partner. It was a way to express herself and escape stress. Recently returned from a yoga retreat with her partner, which was peaceful and inspiring. | Described a hike with her partner where they came across a waterfall oasis, which made her feel peaceful and relieved of worries. | Planned to get out in nature again next month, which will be a refreshing experience. | Shared a photo that represents resilience and strength, reminding her to keep growing through any obstacles. | Acknowledged Deborah's compliment and encouraged her to continue finding beauty in life.
